Our Services

What We Offer

At AnalyzedByIITIANS, we provide a wide range of educational services designed to help students excel in their studies. Our services are tailored to meet the needs of learners at different stages, ensuring quality learning and effective exam preparation.

1. Online Courses

We offer comprehensive online courses covering various subjects, especially for competitive exams. These courses are designed by IITians and provide in-depth analysis, quizzes, and assignments to enhance your learning experience.

2. One-on-One Mentoring

Get personalized guidance and support from experienced mentors. Our one-on-one mentoring sessions are focused on addressing your specific learning needs and helping you achieve your academic goals.

3. Study Materials & Resources

Access our vast library of study materials, including notes, solved examples, practice papers, and more. We provide resources that are aligned with the latest exam patterns.

4. Exam Analysis & Feedback

We offer detailed exam analysis and feedback to help students understand their strengths and areas for improvement. This allows you to fine-tune your preparation strategy for better results.

5. Mock Tests

Practice with our mock tests that simulate real exam conditions. These tests help students assess their progress, build confidence, and identify gaps in their knowledge.
